CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 21, 1959, pg. 3, reads: "Victim's Parents - Mr. and Mrs. Freddie Jackson of 2533 Breckenridge [Brackenridge] St., the parents of Freda Jackson, strangulation victim, were present at the Criminal Court as Edward Simpson was sentenced to from 10 to 20 years in Western Penitentiary, because of the slaying. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Jackson and Freddie Jackson, parents of murder victim Freda Jackson, in Allegheny County Courthouse
